  "content": "# document IDs are auto-generated by createDocument never set manually\n\nWhen creating documents via MCP, never pass a manual ID. The `createDocument` tool generates unique IDs automatically.\n\nManual IDs risk collisions, bypass the system's uniqueness guarantees, and may not follow the expected format. The auto-generated ID is returned in the `createDocument` response \u2014 use that for subsequent operations.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[mcp workflows]]\n- [[gotchas]]",
